The Telegraph - Calcutta : Metro

Life

 Twin treat, swim style

 (From top) Dia Mirza and 

 Akshay Kapoor at the second anniversary bash of INOX 

 City Centre; model Tina at a fashion show at Calcutta 

 Swimming Club. Pictures by Aranya Sen and Rashbehari 

 Das

 What: 

 Second anniversary celebrations of INOX City Centre.

 When: Sunday evening.

 The bash: The cast and crew of Alag, comprising actress Dia Mirza, actor Akshay Kapoor, producer Subi Samuel and director Ashu Trikha were present to cut the cake and uncork a bottle of champagne.

 Every patron visiting INOX City Centre on Sunday was treated to a complimentary glass of wine. In a weeklong celebration starting on June 11, guests at the multiplex had the opportunity of winning holiday packages every day. A free ticket with every three tickets bought was also given away on a first-come-first-serve basis.

 Beach beauty

 What: Trend Baywatch, a fashion show by Trend Shoes.

 Where: Calcutta Swimming Club.

 When: June 17, evening.

 Take a look: City models, Tina, Jessica, Ishika, Pamela, Neeraj, Abhoy and Yusuf walked the ramp sporting swimwear. Choreographed by Pinky, the fashion show was a hit with the audience as the models paraded bikinis, swimming trunks and kikoys in floral prints and bright colours. Nakshatra performed the dance interludes and the show culminated with a dance hour led by DJ Harish.




